Tsekeleke is dead in 2017 The Tsekeleke Thola has been battling with his weight for many years and he has sadly lost the battle. Even though his weight is the reason he became famous, he wasn't happy with the weight. Tsekeleke's death was confirmed by his fellow friend and Artist Vetkoek. Vetkoek has confirmed that Tsekeleke died on the 1st of August 2017 around 7 pm. His family called Vetkoek breaking the sad news. Tsekeleke's fans souls have been broken by the breaking of this news.